me.mrCookieSlime.Slimefun.Objects

Class Category

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.mrCookieSlime.Slimefun.Objects.Category
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Keyed
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LockedCategory, SeasonalCategory

    public class Category
extends java.lang.Object
implements Keyed
    Statically handles categories. Represents a category, which structure multiple SlimefunItem in the guide.

    See Categories for the built-in categories.

    Author:
    TheBusyBiscuit
    See Also:
    LockedCategory, SeasonalCategory

      • Category

        public Category(NamespacedKey key,
                ItemStack item)
        Constructs a new Category with the given NamespacedKey as an identifier and the given ItemStack as its display item. The tier is set to a default value of 3.
        Parameters:
        key - The NamespacedKey that is used to identify this Category
        item - The ItemStack that is used to display this Category

      • Category

        public Category(NamespacedKey key,
                ItemStack item,
                int tier)
        Constructs a new Category with the given NamespacedKey as an identifier and the given ItemStack as its display item.
        Parameters:
        key - The NamespacedKey that is used to identify this Category
        item - The ItemStack that is used to display this Category
        tier - The tier of this Category, higher tiers will make this Category appear further down in the SlimefunGuide
